pseudocode for Client

Create Config with default values if it doesn't exist
If it is not readable, terminate gracefully with an error message

Hello user enter your password, send that to the server
recieve error, password incorrect if it is incorrect

recieve server's message of the day

What do you want to do? List files, download file or upload file

if user answer is to list the files
    recieve list of files from the server

if the user answer is to download a file 
    recieve the bytes of the file

if the user wishes to upload a file
    send the bytes of the file

    authenticated user request a list of shared files from the server

end



